olpcMAP,provides,a,free,publicly,available,and,publicly,editable,global,map,of,locations,where,education,technology,is,in,use,This,resource,makes,it,easier,for,educators,and,volunteers,to,connect,with,nearby,technology,projects,The,olpcMAP,API,allows,users,to,insert,maps,of,technology,education,projects,on,their,own,sites,at,various,levels,of,detail,geographic,scope,and,complexity